node.text: Ad - I collaborated with @wacom and got to try the Wacom One. I were suppose to get it in May for @mermay_official, but due to Covid and living in Kenya I got it a bit late. Please forgive the quality - I like drawing more than doing videos 💕 @wacom

node.text:
Here’s the video of my process for my @imagineFX cover (if you wish to see it in real time check it out on their YouTube channel: https://youtu.be/KF_Ektb4fQ8). I hope you’ll find this informative and that it might help to inspire in these uninspiring days.
#staysafe #stayhome  #girlsinanimation

node.text:
A free weekend means time to do some #gouache #painting. I hope you enjoy! #girlsinanimation 
Paints: @holbeinartistmaterials #gouache 
Paper: @archespapers 300g hot pressed

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by PERNILLE ØRUM | Vis Dev on September 20, 2021. May be a cartoon of 1 person.

node.text:
I’ve arrived home and finally back and busy at work. 
I might have hit the ground running but I’m in desperate need of some warming up, so starting up with a familiar lady. #elsa #frozen @disneyanimation #girlsinanimation #itsgoodtobeback

node.text: Orange #mermaid love on a grey Monday 🧡 #girlsinanimation

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by PERNILLE ØRUM | Vis Dev in BaneGaarden. May be an image of footwear.

node.text:
I am emptying out my closet and selling some stuff this Sunday in Copenhagen (see where in location above). I also found a few copies of my book #theartofpernilleorum which I’ll bring as well so if you want a personally signed copy don’t be shy and stop by :) 
I’ll be there 11am - 4pm Sunday Sept 12th. #girlsinanimation

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by PERNILLE ØRUM | Vis Dev on September 09, 2021 tagging @digitalbobert, and @lightboxexpo.

node.text:
This weekend it’s @lightboxexpo and despite all my efforts I have not managed to get ready for it this year. Instead I’ve decided to do next year extremely well and put all my ideas from this year into 2022 (already can’t wait). 
I am going to be on a panel with some amazingly talented people talking about character design (see Saturday’s schedule), so I hope to catch you there.
That being said I’m so excited to see what everyone else have in store and I’m sure that @digitalbobert and his team has made another great online event 🙌 #girlsinanimation #lightboxexpo2021

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by PERNILLE ØRUM | Vis Dev on September 08, 2021. May be an illustration of 1 person and text.

node.text: Both #mermay books are approved and printed. This week they’ll be shipped to my home and I’ll start shipping them out to everyone who ordered the book/books.  Can’t wait to hear what you think! So happy with how they turned out. #girlsinanimation #mermaid #mermaidsinmay #mermaidsinmay2

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by PERNILLE ØRUM | Vis Dev in Denmark. May be a cartoon of one or more people.

node.text:
I have been missing online for quite some time while spending all hours with the little one and family here in Denmark. But in two weeks I’ll be back in Kenya and back at work and I can’t wait. I haven’t had time to draw at all and I miss it so much! 

I plan on doing fan-art to get back into shape. Anything you wish to see? I’ll also make sure to record the process so it’ll be available on Patreon which I’m also excited to get back into ♥️ #girlsinanimation

Had a wonderful chat with @tothemoon_honey today with focus on giving birth, being a freelancer mom and living in Kenya. So much fun ♥️ Make sure to check the podcast when it’s out - information in their profile #tothemoonhoney 
#girlsinanimation
